            "text": "‚ÄúRight-to-work‚Äù legislation is designed to end ‚Äúclosed shop‚Äù arrangements, in which everyone in a unionized workplace is required to join the union and pay dues. Such laws open the door to a financial death spiral for unions, as they are forced to represent free riders without receiving revenue from them.",
